data.description: Welcome to 6005 Aubrey Lee Ln! Located In N. Crestview, This 4BR | 2BA Home Features A Split Floor Plan With An Open Living Concept. The Kitchen Comes Equipped With Granite Countertops, Sleek Black Appliances, Breakfast Bar & Spacious Pantry. From The Kitchen Is An Indoor Laundry Room, Which Leads To The Enclosed Garage That Is Currently Used As A Bonus Room. This Versatile Space Can Serve As An Additional Lounge, Retreat, Crafting Haven, Game Room Or Converted Back To A Garage! Adjacent To The Kitchen Is The Master Suite With Trayed Ceiling & Ensuite Bathroom With A Dual Vanity, Soaking Tub & Separate Shower. There Are 3 Additional Bedrooms & A Full Bathroom. You'll Love The Large Privacy Fenced Backyard, Perfect For Entertaining. No HOA & X Flood Zone Make Owning Affordable!
